title: Free Agency Madness Continues
description:
Matthew Berry, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp discuss the fantasy impact of the latest trades and signings including the Deshaun Watson trade to the Browns and Matt Ryan to the Colts. Plus the guys break down the impact of Davante Adams becoming a Raider, Allen Robinson signing with the Rams, JuJu Smith-Schuster heading to Kansas City and more!
